<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:44
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='393832' id='t-393832'>(Music ends)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:47
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='396711' id='t-396711'>Or take, for example, the phrase
for &quot;It is right&quot; or &quot;It is correct&quot; --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='400726' id='t-400726'>&quot;Lickih nehu ... Lickih nehu.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='402322' id='t-402322'>It's an affirmation, an agreement.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='404979' id='t-404979'>&quot;Lickih nehu.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='406161' id='t-406161'>When I hear that phrase,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='407337' id='t-407337'>something like this starts rolling
