<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='412031' id='t-412031'>(Music and singing &quot;Lickih nehu&quot;)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:10
