<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='419572' id='t-419572'>(Music ends)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:13
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='422199' id='t-422199'>And in both of those cases,
what I did was I took the melody</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='425040' id='t-425040'>and the phrasing
