<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='440037' id='t-440037'>who work intimately
with music and language,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='443099' id='t-443099'>but it's also something I've had
in my head since I was a kid,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='446067' id='t-446067'>how musical my parents sounded</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='448122' id='t-448122'>when they were speaking
to each other and to us.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='452070' id='t-452070'>It was from them
