<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='460011' id='t-460011'>every word, every sentence
that we receive.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='462787' id='t-462787'>Perhaps you can hear it
in the words I'm speaking even now.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:59
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='468237' id='t-468237'>Finally, we go to the 1950s United States</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='470676' id='t-470676'>and the most seminal work
