<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='517739' id='t-517739'>still there is music.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='519825' id='t-519825'>And what is this music?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='522903' id='t-522903'>It was that sneeze in the back.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:56
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='525132' id='t-525132'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:57
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='526702' id='t-526702'>It is the everyday soundscape
that arises from the audience themselves:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='531787' id='t-531787'>their coughs, their sighs, their rustles,
their whispers, their sneezes,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='536080' id='t-536080'>the room, the wood
of the floors and the walls</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='538645' id='t-538645'>expanding and contracting,
creaking and groaning</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='541127' id='t-541127'>with the heat and the cold,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='542555' id='t-542555'>the pipes clanking and contributing.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='547306' id='t-547306'>And controversial though it was,
